24static inline isc_result_t
25fromtext_keydata(ARGS_FROMTEXT) {
26 isc_token_t token;
27 dns_secalg_t alg;
28 dns_secproto_t proto;
29 dns_keyflags_t flags;
30 uint32_t refresh, addhd, removehd;
31
32 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_keydata);
33
34 UNUSED(type);
35 UNUSED(rdclass);
36 UNUSED(origin);
37 UNUSED(options);
38 UNUSED(callbacks);
39
40 /* refresh timer */
41 RETERR(isc_lex_getmastertoken(lexer, &token, isc_tokentype_string,
42 false));
43 RETTOK(dns_time32_fromtext(DNS_AS_STR(token), &refresh));
44 RETERR(uint32_tobuffer(refresh, target));
45
46 /* add hold-down */
47 RETERR(isc_lex_getmastertoken(lexer, &token, isc_tokentype_string,
48 false));
49 RETTOK(dns_time32_fromtext(DNS_AS_STR(token), &addhd));
50 RETERR(uint32_tobuffer(addhd, target));
51
52 /* remove hold-down */
53 RETERR(isc_lex_getmastertoken(lexer, &token, isc_tokentype_string,
54 false));
55 RETTOK(dns_time32_fromtext(DNS_AS_STR(token), &removehd));
56 RETERR(uint32_tobuffer(removehd, target));
57
58 /* flags */
59 RETERR(isc_lex_getmastertoken(lexer, &token, isc_tokentype_string,
60 false));
61 RETTOK(dns_keyflags_fromtext(&flags, &token.value.as_textregion));
62 RETERR(uint16_tobuffer(flags, target));
63
64 /* protocol */
65 RETERR(isc_lex_getmastertoken(lexer, &token, isc_tokentype_string,
66 false));
67 RETTOK(dns_secproto_fromtext(&proto, &token.value.as_textregion));
68 RETERR(mem_tobuffer(target, &proto, 1));
69
70 /* algorithm */
71 RETERR(isc_lex_getmastertoken(lexer, &token, isc_tokentype_string,
72 false));
73 RETTOK(dns_secalg_fromtext(&alg, &token.value.as_textregion));
74 RETERR(mem_tobuffer(target, &alg, 1));
75
76 /* No Key? */
77 if ((flags & 0xc000) == 0xc000)
78 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
79
80 return (isc_base64_tobuffer(lexer, target, -2));
81}
82
83static inline isc_result_t
84totext_keydata(ARGS_TOTEXT) {
85 isc_region_t sr;
86 char buf[sizeof("64000")];
87 unsigned int flags;
88 unsigned char algorithm;
89 unsigned long refresh, add, deltime;
90 char algbuf[DNS_NAME_FORMATSIZE];
91 const char *keyinfo;
92
93 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_keydata);
94
95 if ((tctx->flags & DNS_STYLEFLAG_KEYDATA) == 0 || rdata->length < 16)
96 return (unknown_totext(rdata, tctx, target));
97
98 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &sr);
99
100 /* refresh timer */
101 refresh = uint32_fromregion(&sr);
102 isc_region_consume(&sr, 4);
103 RETERR(dns_time32_totext(refresh, target));
104 RETERR(str_totext(" ", target));
105
106 /* add hold-down */
107 add = uint32_fromregion(&sr);
108 isc_region_consume(&sr, 4);
109 RETERR(dns_time32_totext(add, target));
110 RETERR(str_totext(" ", target));
111
112 /* remove hold-down */
113 deltime = uint32_fromregion(&sr);
114 isc_region_consume(&sr, 4);
115 RETERR(dns_time32_totext(deltime, target));
116 RETERR(str_totext(" ", target));
117
118 /* flags */
119 flags = uint16_fromregion(&sr);
120 isc_region_consume(&sr, 2);
121 snprintf(buf, sizeof(buf), "%u", flags);
122 RETERR(str_totext(buf, target));
123 RETERR(str_totext(" ", target));
124 if ((flags & DNS_KEYFLAG_KSK) != 0) {
125 if ((flags & DNS_KEYFLAG_REVOKE) != 0) {
126 keyinfo = "revoked KSK";
127 } else {
128 keyinfo = "KSK";
129 }
130 } else {
131 keyinfo = "ZSK";
132 }
133
134 /* protocol */
135 snprintf(buf, sizeof(buf), "%u", sr.base[0]);
136 isc_region_consume(&sr, 1);
137 RETERR(str_totext(buf, target));
138 RETERR(str_totext(" ", target));
139
140 /* algorithm */
141 algorithm = sr.base[0];
142 snprintf(buf, sizeof(buf), "%u", algorithm);
143 isc_region_consume(&sr, 1);
144 RETERR(str_totext(buf, target));
145
146 /* No Key? */
147 if ((flags & 0xc000) == 0xc000)
148 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
149
150 /* key */
151 if ((tctx->flags & DNS_STYLEFLAG_MULTILINE) != 0)
152 RETERR(str_totext(" (", target));
153 RETERR(str_totext(tctx->linebreak, target));
154 if (tctx->width == 0) /* No splitting */
155 RETERR(isc_base64_totext(&sr, 60, "", target));
156 else
157 RETERR(isc_base64_totext(&sr, tctx->width - 2,
158 tctx->linebreak, target));
159
160 if ((tctx->flags & DNS_STYLEFLAG_RRCOMMENT) != 0)
161 RETERR(str_totext(tctx->linebreak, target));
162 else if ((tctx->flags & DNS_STYLEFLAG_MULTILINE) != 0)
163 RETERR(str_totext(" ", target));
164
165 if ((tctx->flags & DNS_STYLEFLAG_MULTILINE) != 0)
166 RETERR(str_totext(")", target));
167
168 if ((tctx->flags & DNS_STYLEFLAG_RRCOMMENT) != 0) {
169 isc_region_t tmpr;
170 char rbuf[ISC_FORMATHTTPTIMESTAMP_SIZE];
171 char abuf[ISC_FORMATHTTPTIMESTAMP_SIZE];
172 char dbuf[ISC_FORMATHTTPTIMESTAMP_SIZE];
173 isc_time_t t;
174
175 RETERR(str_totext(" ; ", target));
176 RETERR(str_totext(keyinfo, target));
177 dns_secalg_format((dns_secalg_t) algorithm, algbuf,
178 sizeof(algbuf));
179 RETERR(str_totext("; alg = ", target));
180 RETERR(str_totext(algbuf, target));
181 RETERR(str_totext("; key id = ", target));
182 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &tmpr);
183 /* Skip over refresh, addhd, and removehd */
184 isc_region_consume(&tmpr, 12);
185 snprintf(buf, sizeof(buf), "%u",
186 dst_region_computeid(&tmpr));
187 RETERR(str_totext(buf, target));
188
189 if ((tctx->flags & DNS_STYLEFLAG_MULTILINE) != 0) {
190 isc_stdtime_t now;
191
192 isc_stdtime_get(&now);
193
194 RETERR(str_totext(tctx->linebreak, target));
195 RETERR(str_totext("; next refresh: ", target));
196 isc_time_set(&t, refresh, 0);
197 isc_time_formathttptimestamp(&t, rbuf, sizeof(rbuf));
198 RETERR(str_totext(rbuf, target));
199
200 if (add == 0U) {
201 RETERR(str_totext(tctx->linebreak, target));
202 RETERR(str_totext("; no trust", target));
203 } else {
204 RETERR(str_totext(tctx->linebreak, target));
205 if (add < now) {
206 RETERR(str_totext("; trusted since: ",
207 target));
208 } else {
209 RETERR(str_totext("; trust pending: ",
210 target));
211 }
212 isc_time_set(&t, add, 0);
213 isc_time_formathttptimestamp(&t, abuf,
214 sizeof(abuf));
215 RETERR(str_totext(abuf, target));
216 }
217
218 if (deltime != 0U) {
219 RETERR(str_totext(tctx->linebreak, target));
220 RETERR(str_totext("; removal pending: ",
221 target));
222 isc_time_set(&t, deltime, 0);
223 isc_time_formathttptimestamp(&t, dbuf,
224 sizeof(dbuf));
225 RETERR(str_totext(dbuf, target));
226 }
227 }
228
229 }
230 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
231}

233static inline isc_result_t
234fromwire_keydata(ARGS_FROMWIRE) {
235 isc_region_t sr;
236
237 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_keydata);
238
239 UNUSED(type);
240 UNUSED(rdclass);
241 UNUSED(dctx);
242 UNUSED(options);
243
244 isc_buffer_activeregion(source, &sr);
245 isc_buffer_forward(source, sr.length);
246 return (mem_tobuffer(target, sr.base, sr.length));
247}
248
249static inline isc_result_t
250towire_keydata(ARGS_TOWIRE) {
251 isc_region_t sr;
252
253 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_keydata);
254
255 UNUSED(cctx);
256
257 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &sr);
258 return (mem_tobuffer(target, sr.base, sr.length));
259}

261static inline int
262compare_keydata(ARGS_COMPARE) {
263 isc_region_t r1;
264 isc_region_t r2;
265
266 REQUIRE(rdata1->type == rdata2->type);
267 REQUIRE(rdata1->rdclass == rdata2->rdclass);
268 REQUIRE(rdata1->type == dns_rdatatype_keydata);
269
270 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata1, &r1);
271 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata2, &r2);
272 return (isc_region_compare(&r1, &r2));
273}
274
275static inline isc_result_t
276fromstruct_keydata(ARGS_FROMSTRUCT) {
277 dns_rdata_keydata_t *keydata = source;
278
279 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_keydata);
280 REQUIRE(source != NULL);
281 REQUIRE(keydata->common.rdtype == type);
282 REQUIRE(keydata->common.rdclass == rdclass);
283
284 UNUSED(type);
285 UNUSED(rdclass);
286
287 /* Refresh timer */
288 RETERR(uint32_tobuffer(keydata->refresh, target));
289
290 /* Add hold-down */
291 RETERR(uint32_tobuffer(keydata->addhd, target));
292
293 /* Remove hold-down */
294 RETERR(uint32_tobuffer(keydata->removehd, target));
295
296 /* Flags */
297 RETERR(uint16_tobuffer(keydata->flags, target));
298
299 /* Protocol */
300 RETERR(uint8_tobuffer(keydata->protocol, target));
301
302 /* Algorithm */
303 RETERR(uint8_tobuffer(keydata->algorithm, target));
304
305 /* Data */
306 return (mem_tobuffer(target, keydata->data, keydata->datalen));
307}
308
309static inline isc_result_t
310tostruct_keydata(ARGS_TOSTRUCT) {
311 dns_rdata_keydata_t *keydata = target;
312 isc_region_t sr;
313
314 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_keydata);
315 REQUIRE(target != NULL);
316
317 keydata->common.rdclass = rdata->rdclass;
318 keydata->common.rdtype = rdata->type;
319 ISC_LINK_INIT(&keydata->common, link);
320
321 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &sr);
322
323 /* Refresh timer */
324 if (sr.length < 4)
325 return (ISC_R_UNEXPECTEDEND);
326 keydata->refresh = uint32_fromregion(&sr);
327 isc_region_consume(&sr, 4);
328
329 /* Add hold-down */
330 if (sr.length < 4)
331 return (ISC_R_UNEXPECTEDEND);
332 keydata->addhd = uint32_fromregion(&sr);
333 isc_region_consume(&sr, 4);
334
335 /* Remove hold-down */
336 if (sr.length < 4)
337 return (ISC_R_UNEXPECTEDEND);
338 keydata->removehd = uint32_fromregion(&sr);
339 isc_region_consume(&sr, 4);
340
341 /* Flags */
342 if (sr.length < 2)
343 return (ISC_R_UNEXPECTEDEND);
344 keydata->flags = uint16_fromregion(&sr);
345 isc_region_consume(&sr, 2);
346
347 /* Protocol */
348 if (sr.length < 1)
349 return (ISC_R_UNEXPECTEDEND);
350 keydata->protocol = uint8_fromregion(&sr);
351 isc_region_consume(&sr, 1);
352
353 /* Algorithm */
354 if (sr.length < 1)
355 return (ISC_R_UNEXPECTEDEND);
356 keydata->algorithm = uint8_fromregion(&sr);
357 isc_region_consume(&sr, 1);
358
359 /* Data */
360 keydata->datalen = sr.length;
361 keydata->data = mem_maybedup(mctx, sr.base, keydata->datalen);
362 if (keydata->data == NULL)
363 return (ISC_R_NOMEMORY);
364
365 keydata->mctx = mctx;
366 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
367}
368
369static inline void
370freestruct_keydata(ARGS_FREESTRUCT) {
371 dns_rdata_keydata_t *keydata = (dns_rdata_keydata_t *) source;
372
373 REQUIRE(source != NULL);
374 REQUIRE(keydata->common.rdtype == dns_rdatatype_keydata);
375
376 if (keydata->mctx == NULL)
377 return;
378
379 if (keydata->data != NULL)
380 isc_mem_free(keydata->mctx, keydata->data);
381 keydata->mctx = NULL;
382}

384static inline isc_result_t
385additionaldata_keydata(ARGS_ADDLDATA) {
386 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_keydata);
387
388 UNUSED(rdata);
389 UNUSED(add);
390 UNUSED(arg);
391
392 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
393}

395static inline isc_result_t
396digest_keydata(ARGS_DIGEST) {
397 isc_region_t r;
398
399 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_keydata);
400
401 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &r);
402
403 return ((digest)(arg, &r));
404}
